org.onap.dcaegen2.services.datafile.config

Class ImmutableAAIClientConfiguration.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.onap.dcaegen2.services.datafile.config.ImmutableAAIClientConfiguration.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ImmutableAAIClientConfiguration

    public static final class ImmutableAAIClientConfiguration.Builder
extends java.lang.Object
    Builds instances of type ImmutableAAIClientConfiguration. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.
